metadata.author: Momma Bear Audio
metadata.description:
Get ready for hours of interactive play with 'Games and Activities by Momma Bear Audio.

With over 3 hours of playtime, this 53-game playlist encourages active listening, decision-making, and fun! From Would You Rather, This or That, Simon Say, and Scavenger Hunts, kids will develop important skills while enjoying a diverse range of entertaining activities. They will have a blast playing along with Ms. Rylee in these fun, engaging, and interactive games.

Games Include: 
-This or That 
-Simon Says 
-How Many Things Can you name 
-Scavenger Hunts 
-Left and Right Body Awareness 
-Would You Rather
-Rhyme Time 
-What is your Favorite
-Talk for one minute 
-Fun Facts 
-Trivia 
-Dive Deep Conversation Starters
